{"id":"806410211613114369","type":"text","timestamp":1769052707,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/806410211613114369","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/witchofthebloodleaftome/805764972340805632\">witchofthebloodleaftome</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/805746154460610560\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>One of my goals in life is to be hot as fuck, but like not a in a heteronormative way.</p><p>I’m not trying to be hot for men.</p><p>I’m hot for myself… and maybe women. </p></blockquote><p>Transbian transition goals mew </p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"805746154460610560"}},{"blog":{"name":"witchofthebloodleaftome"},"post":{"id":"805764972340805632"}}],"baseline_notes":104,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}